[thinking] **Exploring resource calls**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about the lack of metadata in resource calls and whether existing uses of newFactory with dynamic class names might catch UnsupportedFeature errors. I wonder if our test calls could dynamically load the default via Class.forName, considering potential failures. It seems essential to focus on resources and avoid reflection while ensuring that catching errors doesn't interfere with coverage. Also, I'd need to check for any potential interference from commons-logging service files in the classpath. I’ll look into the Htrace project structure too.
